<h2>Privilege rate pay as you go</h2>
<p>If you have a Retired PTAC, you can apply to use pay as you go at priv rate on National Rail services where pay as you go is accepted. Your partner and dependants can also apply if they have a PTAC.</p>
<h3>Applying for privilege rate pay as you go</h3>
<p>You need to get the privilege discount set on another Oyster card - it cannot be set on your Retired Staff Oyster card. Before applying, you must read all the information on the Oyster card privilege discount application form: </p>
