<h2>Staff Travel Cards</h2>
<p>A Staff Travel Card (STC) gives you unlimited free travel on most National Rail services for one day (restrictions apply). These travel cards have replaced the system of free tickets.</p>
<p>You can apply for an STC if you:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Started working for London Transport (excluding staff employed by London Buses), London Regional Transport, or Docklands Light Railway before 1 April 1996</li>
    <li>Have a 1st class PTAC</li>
</ul>
<p>You need to complete an STC application and send it to Staff Travel at least 20 working days before you need it.</p>
<p>It will be posted to your home address.</p>
